# рџљЂ Phase 1 вЂ“ Environment Setup

## 1. Install Node.js (LTS)

Verify installation:

node -v  
npm -v  

---

## 2. Create Next.js Project

Run:

npx create-next-app@latest portfolio

Select:

- TypeScript в†’ YES  
- ESLint в†’ YES  
- Tailwind в†’ YES  
- App Router в†’ YES  
- src directory в†’ NO  
- Import alias в†’ Default  

---

## 3. Run Locally

cd portfolio  
npm run dev  

Visit:  
http://localhost:3000  

---

# рџ§  Phase 2 вЂ“ Content Planning

