# рџЏ—пёЏ Phase 3 вЂ“ Core Implementation

## 1. layout.tsx

Add metadata:

export const metadata = {
  title: "Your Name вЂ“ AI Software Engineer",
  description: "Machine Learning, Forecasting, Backend Engineering",
};

Wrap body:

<body className="bg-white text-gray-900">

---

## 2. Navbar Component

Include navigation links:

- Home
- Projects
- Research
- Experience
- Contact

Keep minimal, fixed at top.

---

## 3. Hero Section

Include:

- Name (large bold)
- Professional title
- Short positioning paragraph
- CTA buttons

---

## 4. ProjectCard Component

Reusable component with:

- Project Title
- Description
- Tech tags
- Buttons:
  - Live Demo
  - GitHub

---

## 5. Individual Pages

Create:

app/projects/page.tsx  
app/research/page.tsx  
app/experience/page.tsx  
app/contact/page.tsx  

Keep each page clean and structured.

---

# рџЊЌ Phase 4 вЂ“ Domain & Deployment

## 1. Initialize Git

git init  
git add .  
git commit -m "Initial portfolio setup"  

Create repository on GitHub and connect:

git remote add origin https://github.com/username/portfolio.git  
git push -u origin main  

---

## 2. Deploy to Vercel

1. Go to vercel.com  
2. Import GitHub repository  
3. Deploy  

Automatic CI/CD enabled.

---

## 3. Connect Custom Domain

1. Purchase domain (yourname.com)  
2. Go to Vercel в†’ Settings в†’ Domains  
3. Add domain  
4. Update DNS at domain provider  
5. SSL activates automatically  

---

# рџ”Ќ Phase 5 вЂ“ SEO Optimization

